				<td colspan="2"><span>My educated guess is that with every swing of a weapon there is a check to see if it should proc.  
<br />

<br />
I base this on observations I've made.  I can have a weapon proc once in a 4 minute melee .. and 3 times in a 30 second melee.  I dont belive that weapons proc X per  minute .. but rather  a weapon has X% chance to proc every swing (swing, not hit.. I've had weapons proc on a miss).  If what I belive is true, then haste does effect procs... in as much as ... you are swining more often, therefor having a greater chance of a proc.</span></td>
