				<td colspan="2"><span>I cannot add raw data to this discussion, I can simply report what I see elsewhere.  The Warrior boards are, as you might imagine, very interested in this issue.
<br />

<br />
Consensus opinion there is that haste does NOT affect proc rates.  Dex does, WA does, but haste does not.
<br />

<br />
I understand your logic, Velv, and it makes sense to me.  But the consensus among people who spend a lot of time studying it is that it doesn't work that way.  When your rate of attack goes up, your proc rate adjusts to compensate, in a manner I do not understand.</span></td>
